            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.4.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new in 0.4.0</h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Open at login</b> — start FocusOS automatically when you sign in (Settings → General).</li>
<li><b>Smarter break pausing</b> — eye breaks now hold during any call, including browser meetings like Google Meet, and while you're screen recording.</li>
<li><b>Redesigned eye break</b> — a calm starfield with a breathing cue.</li>
<li><b>Redesigned blocked-site page</b> — shows the site, your focus stats, and a deliberate hold-to-take-a-break.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
